J TOWER 3
Situated at South of BKK1, J tower 3 is the most awaiting project released in 2023 by a well-known Japanese developer followed their success of J City condominium, J tower 1 and J tower 2. J tower 3 is the highest building in Cambodia with 77 floors and 320.5m from the ground. 
Not only its most convenient locations, J tower 3 is offering the first unique spacious family units. All of the units of J tower 3 on its 77 floors are 3 bedroom units ONLY of total 360 units. This has added more valued to this residential project to become a Family-Home experience throughout the building so called a place like “HOME”
